# Ephemeral pipeline output (scrape JSON, rendered wikitext) stays ignored,
# EXCEPT the reviewer's hand-curated Hebrew overrides: mappings.he.yaml carries
# `src: manual` corrections that survive re-runs and seed the all-time merged
# push. Tracking them means a walk's translation work lives in git, not just on
# the operator's laptop. See docs/iter-cycle-review-guide.md.
output/**
!output/**/
!output/**/mappings.he.yaml
__pycache__